public class MountainCarTiling
extends MountainCar
implements TileAbleEnvironment

Sutton's original definition of the mountain car task with tiling. Tiles are basic 2-dim rectangles. See @MountainCarTilingH for a more general version (hyperRectangles with only certain dimensions taken into account)
